<h3 id="trench-warfare">Trench Warfare.</h3>

<p>John reviewed a sociology journal referring to the Live and Let Live strategy that was reported during WWI. Artillery would shoot <em>between</em> the first and second trench lines. In doing so, they demonstrated accuracy, <em>while</em> showing the other side how <em>not</em> to kill or main, while keeping their Generals happy.</p>

